name: Uranium Atomic Metaball split_2
description: v4w.enko - "Uranium Atomic Metaball split_2" is a metaball structure generated from the uranium atomic model concept with metaball algorithm. There are 92 protons and 92 electrons in the atomic structure. The model represents the only one snapshot from the one moment of time when atoms have spontaneous holded in fixed position. Some geometry layers  are  trimmed to see what is the space inside of the object. Possible to scale, rotate, zoom. Augmented reality mode is included with Hicetnunc
